@startuml
title Edit Event Activity

actor Admin
participant "Edit Form (client)" as Client
participant "/api/events/:id (PUT)" as API
participant "Prisma / PostgreSQL" as DB

Admin -> Client : Open Edit page
Client -> API : GET /api/events/:id (prefill)
API -> DB : SELECT event
DB --> API : event data
API --> Client : event data
Admin -> Client : Update fields and Submit
Client -> API : PUT /api/events/:id {payload with ISO datetimes}
API -> DB : UPDATE event
DB --> API : updated event
API --> Client : 200 OK
Client -> Client : router.push(/events/:id)
Client -> Client : router.refresh()

@enduml
